{"tid":2191629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥呼籲僱主鼓勵員工接受普及檢測","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:38:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e73da252164a4d7b178ea0ef15ead21fb8a4b7fe","tid":2191629,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥說，留意到今日其中一宗確診個案是一名餐廳員工，認為如果員工沒有參與檢測，就有可能傳染給同事及客人，說不定會帶來另一個「餐廳群組」。她對餐廳老闆鼓勵和安排員工參與普及檢測表示肯定，亦讚賞員工樂意配合。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥呼籲僱主鼓勵員工接受普及檢測，令大家接待顧客時更放心，亦令政府更有信心逐步放寬其他營業上的限制，令社交生活和經濟活動早日恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548191-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548191-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4jY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=afbd48e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548191-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f6217de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548191-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}